Hi there. Just wanted to give you another update... I Google-Mapped the route taken since a lot of people expressed an interest.<P><a href="http://www.renegadetourist.com/rendezvous.html">http://www.renegadetourist.com/rendezvous.html</a>.<P>Don't know how long my bandwidth will hold out, so I took a screen grab:<P><a href="http://img154.imageshack.us/img154/5098/rendezvousgmaps6ez.jpg">http://img154.imageshack.us/img154/5098/rendezvousgmaps6ez.jpg</a>.</A></B></I>
